## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="80207-114">這個建構函式會建立的規則參照<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>內包含的文法物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-114">This constructor creates a rule reference to an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object within the containing  grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-115">若要建立的規則參考`rule`項目，在外部文法檔案中，使用任何下列的建構函式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-115">To create a rule reference to a `rule` element in an external grammar file, use any of the following constructors:</span></span>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="80207-116">下列範例會建立可辨識片語的文法"曾榮獲世界盃民族 is"再加上贏得世界盃比賽的國家/地區名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-116">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-117">在建立後<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>物件`winnerRule`並提供字串識別碼`WorldCupWinner`，此範例會將字串附加 「 贏得比賽世界盃國家/地區 」 規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-117">After creating the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object `winnerRule` and giving it the string identifier `WorldCupWinner`, the example appends the string  "A nation that has won the World Cup is" to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-118">使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>物件，此範例會建置一份歐洲國家 （地區） 和一份南美洲國家/地區，並將每個清單加入至其個別的規則，`ruleEurope`或`ruleSAmerica`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-118">Using <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects, the example then builds a list of European countries and a list of South American countries, and adds each list to its respective rule, `ruleEurope` or `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-119">這個範例會建立的規則參照`ruleEurope`並`ruleSAmerica`並將其加入`WorldCupWinner`規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-119">The example then creates rule references for `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica` and adds them to the `WorldCupWinner` rule.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="80207-120">建立的文法的格式如下。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-120">The created grammar has the following form.</span></span>  
  
```  
<grammar version="1.0" xml:lang="en-US" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/06/grammar" root="WorldCupWinner">  
    <rule id="WorldCupWinner" scope="public">  
        <item> A nation that has won the world cup is </item>  
        <one-of>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#EuropeanNations" />  
            </item>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#SouthAmericanNations" />  
            </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="EuropeanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> England </item>  
            <item> France </item>  
            <item> Germany </item>  
            <item> Italy </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="SouthAmericanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> Argentina </item>  
            <item> Brazil </item>  
            <item> Uruguay </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
</grammar>  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="80207-125">這個建構函式會建立外部文法檔案的規則參考。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-125">This constructor creates a rule reference to an external grammar file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-126">URI 可能也會包含參考，例如，某規則的識別項`http://www.contoso.com/ExternalGrammar.grxml#targetRule`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-126">The URI may also include the identifier of a rule to reference, for example `http://www.contoso.com/ExternalGrammar.grxml#targetRule`.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="80207-127">如果`uri`參數未指定的規則識別項規則參考會指向目標文法根規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-127">If the `uri` parameter does not specify a rule identifier, the rule reference points to the root rule of the target grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-128">若要建立的規則參考<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>物件內相同的文法，請使用任何下列的建構函式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-128">To create a rule reference to an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object within the same grammar, use any of the following constructors:</span></span>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="80207-129">下列範例會建立傳回匯流排接駁車服務的相關資訊的應用程式的文法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-129">The following example creates a grammar for an application that returns information about bus shuttle service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-130">第一種方法， `GrammarUrlForRoute`，是一個字串，指定路由，並將其附加至字串，指定位置的文法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-130">The first method, `GrammarUrlForRoute`, takes a string that specifies a route and appends it to a string specifying the location of a grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-131">這會指定該文法中的特定規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-131">This specifies a particular rule in that grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-132">此方法會傳回`Uri`該規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-132">The method returns a `Uri` for that rule.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="80207-133">第二個方法中， `CreateGrammarForRoute`，建立<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>名為的項目`grammar`所指定的規則參考`Uri`傳遞給它的`GrammarUrlForRoute`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-133">The second method, `CreateGrammarForRoute`, creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> element named `grammar` with a rule reference specified by the `Uri` passed to it by `GrammarUrlForRoute`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-134">請注意，名為 _route 變數封入類別的成員。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-134">Note that the variable named _route is a member of an enclosing class.</span></span>  
  
```  
private Uri GrammarUrlForRoute(string route)  
{  
  return new Uri("http://localhost/MyBus/MyBusLocations.grxml#LocationsForRoute" + route);  
}  
  
private SrgsDocument CreateGrammarForRoute()  
{  
  SrgsDocument grammar = new SrgsDocument();  
  grammar.Mode = SrgsGrammarMode.Voice;  
  SrgsRule rule = new SrgsRule("LocationsForRoute" + _route);  
  SrgsRuleRef ruleref = new SrgsRuleRef(GrammarUrlForRoute(_route));  
  
  SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag tag = new SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag ("$.Location = $$");  
  
  rule.Elements.Add(ruleref);  
  rule.Elements.Add(tag);  
  grammar.Rules.Add(rule);  
  grammar.Root = rule;  
  return grammar;  
}  
```  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="80207-135">名為 _ 的變數`route`是未宣告和在上述範例中未定義。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-135">The variable named _`route` is undeclared and undefined in the preceding sample.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="80207-136">它應該宣告為<xref:System.String>和包含特定匯流排路由的路由號碼，才能編譯並執行先前的範例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="80207-136">It should be declared as a <xref:System.String> and contain the route number for a particular bus route before the preceding sample is compiled and run.</span></span>

  
  
